<p><%= @member.name %></p>
<p>
  Thank you for submitting a new Training Category to our lists.
</p>
<p>
  We're pleased to tell you that your submission has been authorized - but with this change:
</p>
<p>
  <% if @category.name_change?(@category.submitted_name) %>
    <%= @category.report_name_change(@category.submitted_name) %>
  <% end %>
  <% if @category.group_change?(@category.submitted_group) %>
    <br />
    <%= @category.report_group_change(@category.submitted_group) %>
  <% end %>
</p>
<p>Best wishes<br />
   The Tickets for Training Admin Team</p>
